Add test/resources/.nosearch to keep directory off the load-path

Add test/resources/.nosearch to keep directory off the load-path

Adding this file ensures that the "test/resources/" directory does not
accidentally end up on the `load-path'.  This also helps tools used to
detect the feature provided by a package, which would otherwise claim
that this package provides `dummy-package' and some other dummy
packages that are located here.
